                            <comment id="395760" author="adilger" created="Wed, 6 Dec 2023 20:56:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It looks like this is a duplicate of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17540&quot; title=&quot;sync and delay before LBUG() calls panic()&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-17540&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-17540&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and is fixed by patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/50419&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/50419&lt;/a&gt; &quot;&lt;tt&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15740&quot; title=&quot;runtests test_1: &amp;#39;Space not all freed: now 8932kB, was 8788kB&amp;#39;&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-15740&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-15740&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; tests: scale fs_log_size by OSTCOUNT&lt;/tt&gt;&quot;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;That patch is not landed on b2_12, so this subtest may occasionally fail with 2.12.x clients. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
